t_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20771,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/23\/islam-holding-hot-coal\/","url_meta":{"origin":40064,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Patience: When practicing Islam is like holding a hot coal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA time of patience will come to people in which adhering to one's religion is like grasping a hot coal.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2260 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/04\/allah-sends-trials-benefit\/","url_meta":{"origin":40064,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Allah tests those He loves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Mahmud ibn Labid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah loves a people, He afflicts them with trials. Whoever is patient is given patience, and whoever is anxious is given anxiety.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 23641 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8248,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/sabr-believer-mixes-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":40064,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Patience: Believer who mixes with people rewarded more","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer who mixes with people and is patient with their harm has a greater reward than the believer who does not mix with people, nor is patient with their harm.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4032\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24282,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/patience-first-strike-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":40064,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sabr: Reward for patience at first strike is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty says: O son of Adam, if you are patient and restrained at the first shock of calamity, I would not be pleased with any reward for you less than Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1597 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.a